# Data — never commit raw or processed data
data/raw/
data/processed/
data/partitions/

# Models — never commit trained model files
models/

# Logs
logs/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.eggs/

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/
.env

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Results — optional: remove if you want to track results
experiments/results/
```

---

## How to Run — 4 Terminal Workflow
```
Terminal 0          Terminal 1          Terminal 2          Terminal 3
─────────────       ─────────────       ─────────────       ─────────────
run_server.py       run_client.py       run_client.py       run_client.py
                    --bank bank1        --bank bank2        --bank bank3

    │                    │                   │                   │
    │◄────── bank1_round_1.json ─────────────┘                   │
    │◄────── bank2_round_1.json ─────────────────────────────────┘
    │◄────── bank3_round_1.json ─────────────────────────────────┘
    │
    │── JSON Tree Concatenation Algorithm ──►
    │
    │──── global_model_round_1.json ────────►│───────────────────►
    │                                        │                   │
    [Repeat for Rounds 2 → 5]